INSTALL

1. Requirements
===============

* You need SDL, SDL_ttf and libxml2 to compile and run this program.
   - SDL:
     http://www.libsdl.org/
   - SDL_ttf:
     http://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_ttf/
   - libxml2:
     http://www.xmlsoft.org/

2. Default installation
=======================

Compile paxman with
$ make

you can install it with
$ make install

and deinstall it with
$ make deinstall

3. Known problems
=================

In some cases xmlmemory.h and parser.h won't be found.
You have to copy the libxml2 header files to a different
directory.

e.g.:
$ cp -R /usr/include/libxml2/libxml /usr/include

